OL,5, Three women have spoken of their relief
OL,6, after the man who repeatedly raped and 
OL,7, coercively controlled them was given a 
OL,8, 32-year sentence.                      
OL,10,FRobert Parkin was investigated after   
OL,11,Fhis ex-girlfriend Nicola Green reported
OL,12,Fhim to police, which encouraged the    
OL,13,Fother two women to come forward.       
OL,15,FThey had all been in relationships with
OL,16,Fhim, and wanted him jailed in order to 
OL,17,Fstop him from harming any more women.  
OL,19,FThe judge praised the women for their  
OL,20,F"amazing courage".                     
